{"id": "1493649157338956026", "channel_id": "1493649157338956026", "type": 0, "author_id": "1340549333359132753", "author_name": "150_ripe", "author_bot": false, "content": "拿忘却前夜主旋律改了一下（主要是练习），前几天听班里艺术生的去学了卡农，旋律可能有借鉴吧……有大佬再帮忙改改<:pray:1356053116260454534> \n\n用的musescore，钢琴声听着有点硬，但我不会调音色<:takenotes:1357186646294138890> 谱子里有两个钢琴，旋律之间有交错，是为了方便调力度，谱中的力度记号都是在混音器调过后标的（不会混音），可能光看谱子不准。\n\n做这个音乐真是一路坎坷<:takenotes:1357186646294138890> 先是电脑死机，然后是耳机左声道直接消失，最后是显示器断连<:dead:1356082627509092372> \n\n~~我是不是同人区里第一个做音乐的~~", "timestamp": "2026-04-14T16:28:29.769000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [{"id": "1493649157662052614", "filename": "6c7485cce8deaf12.pdf", "content_type": "application/pdf", "size": 188304, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1493649157338956026/1493649157662052614/6c7485cce8deaf12.pdf?ex=69dfbcad&is=69de6b2d&hm=3d15ca85bc028ad774e27b7b982a63730de34f36fbe83c01722735f8e81ec05e&"}, {"id": "1493649158203248731", "filename": "d93fc6cc753d139c.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 2961239, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1493649157338956026/1493649158203248731/d93fc6cc753d139c.mp3?ex=69dfbcad&is=69de6b2d&hm=20beae60b726fb570c43bc40401847d7e98a97821dd01629f0df9c4999ccc8df&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1493649157338956026", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "改编曲", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811"]}
